            <title><![CDATA[Split Fiction Dev Says Studio Will Never Implement Microtransactions In Its Games]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/split-fiction-dev-says-studio-will-never-implement-microtransactions-in-its-games/1100-6529775/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
